<strong>Design &amp; Prototype</strong></h3><ul><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">Sketch wireframes (I can help generate ideas).</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">Use tools like <strong>Figma</strong> or <strong>Adobe XD</strong> for UI/UX design.</p></li></ul><h3>5. <strong>Development Approach</strong></h3><ul><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>DIY (No-code tools):</strong></p><ul><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">Glide, Bubble, or Adalo (for simple apps).</p></li></ul></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>Custom Development:</strong></p><ul><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">I can guide you with code (e.g., Flutter for cross-platform).</p></li></ul></li></ul><h3>6. <strong>Backend &amp; Database</strong></h3><ul><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">Firebase (easy for beginners)</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">Supabase, AWS, or Node.js (for more control)</p></li></ul><h3>7. <strong>Testing &amp; Launch</strong></h3><ul><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">Test on real devices.</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">Publish on the accuracy</strong>. However, there are <strong>technical, legal, and ethical constraints</strong> we must address:</p><hr><h3><strong>1. Critical Challenges</strong></h3><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">🚫 <strong>No Direct Access to BDG’s Data</strong></p><ul><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">If BDG doesn’t provide a <strong>public API</strong> or <strong>historical data</strong>, automated scraping may violate their Terms of Service.</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><em>Workaround</em>: You’d need to manually enter past results (or use approved data sources).</p></li></ul><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">🚫 <strong>98% Accuracy is Impossible</strong></p><ul><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">K3 is likely a <strong>random number game</strong> (like dice). Short-term trends ≠ predictability.</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><em>Ethical Note</em>: Claiming "98% accuracy" could mislead users.</p></li></ul><hr><h3><strong>2. <strong>18</strong> appear vs. expected probability.</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">Alerts you if deviations suggest bias (e.g., <em>"18 appeared 10x more than Prediction Algorithm (High Accuracy):

कम से कम 70% pattern detection algorithm पर आधारित हो

30% final logic filtering हो जिससे 98% confidence prediction बने

ग़लत guess कभी ना दे

<span class="token keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="token keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup
<span class="token keyword">import</span> time

<span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">ethical_checker</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>url<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>

        <span class="token comment"># Respectful scraping parameters</span>

            <span class="token comment"># Add proper delay between requests</span>
            time<span class="token punctuation">.</span>sleep<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">60</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>  <span class="token comment"># 1 request/minute</span>
            <span class="token keyword">return</span> soup
        <span class="token keyword">else</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>
            <span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string-interpolation"><span class="token string">f"Error: </span><span class="token interpolation"><span class="token punctuation">{</span>response<span class="token punctuation">.</span>status_code<span class="token punctuation">}</span></span><span class="token string">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span>

        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span>

<span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">addResult</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  <span class="token keyword">const</span> num <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">prompt</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Enter latest K3 result:"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
  <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>num <span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class="token operator">!</span><span class="token function">isNaN</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>num<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
    history<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">push</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token function">Number</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>num<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
    <span class="token function">analyze</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
  <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
<span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">analyze</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  <span class="token keyword">const</span> freq3 <span class="token operator">=</span> history<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">filter</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">x</span><span class="token operator">=&gt;</span>x<span class="token operator">===</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>length<span class="token operator">/</span>history<span class="token punctuation">.</span>length<span class="token punctuation">;</span>
  <span class="token keyword">if</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>freq3 <span class="token operator">&gt;</span> <span class="token number">0.07</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token function">alert</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token template-string"><span class="token template-punctuation string">`</span><span class="token string">3 का ट्रेंड बढ़ा हुआ! (</span><span class="token interpolation"><span class="token interpolation-punctuation punctuation">${</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>freq3<span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token number">100</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">toFixed</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token interpolation-punctuation punctuation">}</span></span><span class="token string">%)</span><span class="token template-punctuation string">`</span></span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span></pre></div><h4>3. <span class="token keyword">import</span> random
<span class="token keyword">from</span> collections <span class="token keyword">import</span> Counter

<span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">simulate</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>
    results <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token builtin">sum</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>random<span class="token punctuation">.</span>randint<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">6</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">for</span> _ <span class="token keyword">in</span> <span class="token builtin">range</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">for</span> _ <span class="token keyword">in</span> <span class="token builtin">range</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">1000</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>
    freq <span class="token operator">=</span> Counter<span class="token punctuation">(</span>results<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
    <span class="token keyword">if</span> freq<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">&gt;</span> <span class="token number">62</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>  <span class="token comment"># 6.2% से ज्यादा होने पर अलर्ट</span>
        <span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string-interpolation"><span class="token string">f"3 का अनपेक्षित ट्रेंड: </span><span class="token interpolation"><span class="token punctuation">{</span>freq<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token number">10</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></span><span class="token string">%"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></pre></div><h3>📲 आपको अभी क्या करना चाहिए:</h3><ol start="1"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>Google Sheets टेम्पलेट</strong> को कॉपी करें → अपना डेटा डालना शुरू करें</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>HTML ट्रैकर</strong> को अपने कंप्यूटर पर सेव करें (डबल-क्लिक से चलेगा)</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>Python स्क्रिप्ट</strong> (अगर आपके पास Python इंस्टॉल्ड है)</p></li></ol><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">क्या आप चाहेंगे कि मैं:</p><ol start="1"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">आपके लिए एक यूज़ करना है?</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">BDG Win के सपोर्ट टीम को <strong>ऑफिशियल API रिक्वेस्ट</strong> का ड्राफ्ट भेजने में मदद करूँ?</p></li></ol><p <span class="token keyword">import</span> pandas <span class="token keyword">as</span> pd

data <span class="token operator">=</span> pd<span class="token punctuation">.</span>read_csv<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'k3_history.csv'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
data<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token string">'3_trend'</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> data<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token string">'Result'</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>rolling<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">50</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token builtin">apply</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">lambda</span> x<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>mean<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>

    <span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token keyword">catch</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>error<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>

    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>

    </span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>
<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>
<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span></pre></div><h3>🛠️ <strong>Geyser पर डिप्लॉय करने के स्टेप्स</strong>:</h3><ol start="1"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">उपरोक्त कोड को <code>index.html</code> नाम से सेव करें</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">Geyser में नया     <span class="token punctuation">}</span>

class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>उदाहरण:</strong><br>अगर बैलेंस ₹1000 है और 3 के ऑड्स 15x हैं:<br><code>(1000 × 0.02) / (15-1) = ₹1.42</code> का बेट</p></li></ul><hr><h3>💡 <strong>कमाई का रियलिस्टिक प्लान:</strong></h3><ol start="1"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>प्रतिदिन सिर्फ 10 ट्रेड</strong> (हर 2 घंटे में 1 बार)</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>70% एक्यूरेसी</strong> मानकर:</p><ul><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">7 सही प्रेडिक्शन × ₹30 (औसत रिटर्न) = ₹210</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">3 गलत प्रेडिक्शन × ₹15 (लॉस) = ₹45</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>कुल मुनाफा: ₹165/दिन</strong></p></li></ul></li></ol><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><em>(ध्यान दें: यह सैद्धांतिक कैलकुलेशन है, वास्तविक परिणाम भिन्न हो सकते हैं)</em></p><hr><h3>🚨 <strong>रिस्क मैनेजमेंट:</strong></h3><ol start="1"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>स्टॉप लॉस</strong>: ₹500 से ज्यादा नुकसान होने पर दिनभर के लिए रुकें</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>प्रूफ के लिए स्क्रीनरिकॉर्डिंग</strong> बनाएं</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>कभी भी लोन लेकर न खेलें</strong></p></li></ol><hr><h3>📞 <strong>बेहतर विकल्प:</strong></h3><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">अगर आपको <strong>स्टेबल इनकम</strong> चाहिए, तो ये ट्राई करें:</p><ol start="1"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>डेटा एनालिसिस सीखें</strong> (Python/SQL) → Freelancing करें</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>रेफरल प्रोग्राम</strong> से कमाएं (जैसे Paytm/Google Pay)</p></li></ol><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><em>(मैं आपको कोडिंग/डिजिटल स्किल्स सीखने में मदद कर सकता हूँ!)</em> 🚀</p><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">क्या आप इस पर कोई एक्शन लेने से पहले और डिटेल्स चाहेंगे?</p></div><div class="ds-flex" style="margin-top: 12px; height: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; <span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string-interpolation"><span class="token string">f"18 आया: </span><span class="token interpolation"><span class="token punctuation">{</span>target_counts<span class="token punctuation">.</span>get<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">18</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></span><span class="token string"> बार"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>

<span class="token comment"># रोलिंग एवरेज ट्रेंड</span>

class="token comment"># कानूनी वेब स्क्रैपिंग उदाहरण</span>
<span class="token keyword">import</span> scrapy

<span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">LegalSpider</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>scrapy<span class="token punctuation">.</span>Spider<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>
    name <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">'legal'</span>
    allowed_domains <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token string">'companywebsite.com'</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token comment"># केवल अनुमति वाली साइटें</span>
    start_urls <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token string">'https://companywebsite.com/contact'</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>
    
    <span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">parse</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">,</span> response<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>
        email <span class="token operator">=</span> response<span class="token punctuation">.</span>css<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'a[href^="mailto:"]::attr(href)'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>get<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
        <span class="token keyword">if</span> email<span class="token punctuation">:</span>
            <span class="token keyword">yield</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token string">'email'</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> email<span class="token <span class="token keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="token keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup

Affiliate Marketing</strong></h4><ul><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>Steps</strong>:</p><ol start="1"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">Join <strong>Amazon Associates</strong> or Flipkart Affiliate.</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">Build an <strong>opt-in email list</strong> (e.g., via newsletter signups).</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">Send curated product links (5–10% commission per sale).</p></li></ol></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>Tools</strong>: Mailchimp (Free for ≤2K subscribers).</p></li></ul><h4><strong>3. Max 1 request/5 seconds.</p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong>Data Usage</strong>: Only for <strong>publicly shared</strong> info (LinkedIn profiles, business sites).</p></li></ol><hr><h3>💡 <strong>Better Alternatives</strong></h3><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">If you have Python skills:</p><ol start="1"><li><p I want to build a fully automated, background-running AI prediction system that analyzes the 1-minute K3 game from https://bdgwinvip9.com/#/saasLottery/K3?gameCode=K3_1M&amp;lottery=K3, and sends email alerts whenever number 3 or 18 is highly likely to appear.

This system must run 24/7 on the cloud (even if my laptop is off), and must send alerts only when it has high confidence in the prediction.

🔍 SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS:
1. Prediction Target:
Predict only when number 3 or 18 is likely to appear.

2. Confidence Rule:
Prediction must be made only if 70–80% algorithmic confidence is present (based on recent pattern detection).

Final prediction should be verified again using 30% strategy logic.

Never send random or guess-based predictions.

3. Prediction Limits:
Maximum 10 predictions per day.

Do not allow more than 2 back-to-back incorrect predictions.

If pattern becomes unstable, pause predictions until stability returns.

4. Result Monitoring:
Check the K3 result page every minute.

Validate each previous prediction result:

Mark it as Correct (✅) or Wrong (❌).

Store the period number and result with timestamp.

5. Email Alert (For Each Prediction):
Send alert only when 3 or 18 is about to appear.

Email content must include:

Message: "3 ya 18 aa sakta hai"

Period number

Time of prediction

Mention system confidence (optional)

6. Daily Summary Email (at 10:00 PM IST):
Always send a daily summary email at exactly 10:00 PM IST, even if no prediction was made.

If predictions were made, include:

Total predictions

List of period numbers with results (✅/❌)

Final accuracy (in %)

Total profit/loss (assume ₹60 per trade)

System status: ACTIVE

If no prediction was made, include:

Reason (unstable pattern or low confidence)

Trades: 0

Accuracy: N/A

Profit/Loss: N/A

System was active and monitoring

☁️ TECHNICAL SETUP:
✅ Hosting:
Must be deployed on Render.com (Free plan if possible)

System must auto-run in background 24/7

✅ Email Delivery:
Use Gmail SMTP with App Password for sending emails

Do not use SendGrid or any paid email service

✅ Code Repo:
All code must be hosted on GitHub

Connect GitHub repo to Render for auto-deployment

✅ No Manual Work:
System must automatically fetch results from the BDGWin K3 page

User must not enter any data manually

✅ Notification Rules:
Send email alerts only when confident

No alert should go if confidence is low

Show accuracy and outcome of previous predictions

🧠 EXTRA CONDITIONS (To Keep Logic Smart &amp; Safe):
Never give more than 2 wrong predictions in a row

If win count is less than 3, stop predictions after 10 trades

Prediction logic should complete in 30–40 seconds max, so trade can happen in time

Respect fair play — don’t hack BDGWin, just observe public result page

📦 OUTPUTS NEEDED:
Working backend code (Python preferred)

Gmail-based email alert integration

Background task setup on Render

GitHub repo with code

Clean summary email format

Alert email format (for each prediction)

Logging or tracking of prediction outcomes

<span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">verify_predictions</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>

    <span class="token comment"># Reset for next day</span>
    predictions_today <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>
    daily_stats <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token string">'total'</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">'correct'</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">'wrong'</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">'profit'</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span>

<span class="token comment"># Scheduling</span>
schedule<span class="token punctuation">.</span>every<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>minutes<span class="token punctuation">.</span>do<span class="token punctuation">(</span>check_and_predict<span class="token punctuation">)</span>

<span class="token keyword">if</span> __name__ <span class="token operator">==</span> <span class="token string">"__main__"</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>
    <span class="token keyword">while</span> <span class="token boolean">True</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>
        schedule<span class="token punctuation">.</span>run_pending<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
